Package: CNAqc
Type: Package
Title: CNAqc - Copy Number Analysis quality check
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Giulio Caravagna
Maintainer: Giulio Caravagna <gcaravagn@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Giulio", "Caravagna", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gcaravagn@gmail.com")
Description: CNAqc is a package that implements QC metrics and plots to assess the quality of Copy Number calls. 
  The package provides statistical measures to quantify the concordance between mutation and Copy Number calls,
  exploiring the relation between allelic imbalance in CNA segements and allelic frequencies of somatic mutations. 
